Developing for local use in and around El Dorado County, CA - 
 Requirements
  Easy to install and use
  Few to no transaction fees for users
 Features
  Immediately exchangeable for GEM goods and services
  Provide payment platform for otherwise unaffordable classes, workshops, et cetera
  Back by a store of dollar, Ethereum, and/or and physical value which users will commit   

Process
 Create testnet 
  Develop working code for all desired features
 ICO
  Sale of hardware wallets to GEM customers
  Include info on blockchain currencies generally
  Focus on core users, rather than anonymous Internet buyers

